import React from 'react' function Liftar({ barnLift, expr, fjl, mellanLift, liikavaara, barnReady, exprReady, fjlReady, mellanReady, liikavaaraReady }) { // Lifts open/ready/closed status dots const bbDots = barnLift === "1" ? statusDotsOpen : barnReady === "0" ? statusDotsReady : statusDotsClosed; const exDots = expr === "1" ? statusDotsOpen : exprReady === "1" ? statusDotsReady : statusDotsClosed; const fjDots = fjl === "1" ? statusDotsOpen : fjlReady === "1" ? statusDotsReady : statusDotsClosed; const mlDots = mellanLift === "1" ? statusDotsOpen : mellanReady === "1" ? statusDotsReady : statusDotsClosed; const slDots = liikavaara === "1" ? statusDotsOpen : liikavaaraReady === "1" ? statusDotsReady : statusDotsClosed; // Lifts open/ready/closed text const liftOpen = Öppen ; const liftReady = Startklar ; const liftClosed = Stängd ; const bb = barnLift === "1" ? liftOpen : barnReady === "0" ? liftReady : liftClosed; const ex = expr === "1" ? liftOpen : exprReady === "1" ? liftReady : liftClosed; const fj = fjl === "1" ? liftOpen : fjlReady === "1" ? liftReady : liftClosed; const ml = mellanLift === "1" ? liftOpen : mellanReady === "1" ? liftReady : liftClosed; const sl = liikavaara === "1" ? liftOpen : liikavaaraReady === "1" ? liftReady : liftClosed; return (

Liftar

Transportbandet {bb}

Dundret Express {ex}

Fjälliften {fjDots} {fj}

Mellanliften {mlDots} {ml}

Liikavaaraliften {slDots} {sl}

) } export default Liftar
